# Testing and make targets

Use the existing make targets. Do not create ad-hoc test scripts.

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| Verify SCAD + viewer | `make verify-web-ui` |
| API + e2e test | `make test-web` |
| Full Docker stack | `make kbr-test` |
| Inspect running app | `make inspect-ui` |
